Package main

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    CSVHandler
    CSVHandler is class for reading from and writing to the csv files.
    Menu
    The Menu is a command line user interface system cooperating with PCMSystem class
    Owner
    The owner is a class that stores information about a property owner
    Payment
    This class stores information on payments for tax due
    PCMSystem
    PCMSystem decides between GUI and CLI menu to run
    Property
    The Property class stores details about a property based on an information from the csv files.
    TaxCalculator
    The TaxCalculator class is used to calculate tax for a given property
    TaxManager
    The TaxManager provides management functionality such as viewing tax statistics for Department of Environment and has its own modifiable instance of TaxCalculator
